            "État anxieux, contexte imprévisible ou obligation importante ensuite.": "Anxious state, unpredictable context, or important obligation afterward.",
            "Grossesse, adolescence ou antécédents psychiatriques sans avis professionnel.": "Pregnancy, adolescence, or psychiatric history without professional advice.",
            "Crise d'angoisse ou de paranoïa qui ne redescend pas, confusion importante.": "Anxiety or paranoia attack that does not come down, significant confusion.",
